Privacy Policy for Trufo

Last Updated: [Date]

Introduction

Trufo ("us," "we," or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy (the "Policy") explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you access or use the Trufo mobile application (the "App"). By using the App, you agree to this Policy. Please read it carefully to understand how we manage your data.

Information We Collect

We collect different types of information, including:

Personal Information: This may include your name, email address, phone number, and other data you provide when using the App.
Usage Information: We gather data on how you interact with the App, such as your IP address, device type, and usage patterns.
How We Collect Information

We collect information in the following ways:

Directly from You: You may provide us with personal information when using the App.
Automatically: We collect data automatically as you use the App, including through cookies, web beacons, and similar technologies.
How We Use Your Information

We use your information for the following purposes:

To provide you with our App and its services.
To improve and personalize your experience with the App.
To send you updates and information.
To respond to your inquiries.
To analyze user trends and gather statistics.
Information Sharing

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties. We may share your data with trusted service providers who assist us in delivering our services.

Security

We take data security seriously and use industry-standard measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices and services. When we make changes, we will revise the "Last Updated" date at the beginning of this Policy. We encourage you to periodically review this page to stay informed about how we are protecting your data.

Contact Information

If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [Your Contact Information].

By using the Trufo App, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

[End of Privacy Policy]

